OL,3,CWarm home discount to be extended to
OL,4,C2.7 million more households
OL,6,FEnergy bill discounts of #150 will be
OL,7,Fextended to another 2.7 million
OL,8,Fhouseholds to help with fuel costs
OL,9,Fnext winter.
OL,11,FThis brings the number of households
OL,12,Feligible for the warm home discount up
OL,13,Fto just over 6 million, the Department
OL,14,Ffor Energy Security and Net Zero
OL,15,F(DESNZ) has confirmed after a
OL,16,Fconsultation.
OL,18,FThe changes remove some restrictions
OL,19,Fon eligibility and mean every bill
OL,20,Fpayer on means-tested benefits will
OL,21,Fqualify.
