OL,6,FSome 900,000 families with children
OL,7,Fand 1.8 million homes in fuel poverty
OL,8,Fare set to benefit from the payment.
OL,10,FPrime Minister Keir Starmer said: "I
OL,11,Fknow families are still struggling
OL,12,Fwith the cost of living, and I know
OL,13,Fthe fear that comes with not being
OL,14,Fable to afford your next bill.
OL,16,F"Providing security and peace of mind
OL,17,Ffor working people is deeply personal
OL,18,Fto me as Prime Minister and
OL,19,Ffoundational for the Plan for Change.
